== 文化關係 == 
巴西是法國在拉美地區的主要[[文化|文化]]和科技合作夥伴。在巴西三大城市[[聖保羅|聖保羅]]、[[里約熱內盧|里約熱內盧]]和[[巴西利亞|巴西利亞]]分別有三所法國中學，總共有2,150名學生（其中1,000人是法國人）<ref name=rush/>。[[法國文化協會|法國文化協會]]在巴西52個城市合共設有74所分會<ref name=rush>{{cite web|url=http://www.diplomatie.gouv.fr/en/country-files_156/brazil_444/france-and-brazil_2515/cultural-scientific-and-technical-cooperation_2634.html |title=France and Brazil - Cultural, scientific and technical cooperation |publisher=Ministry of Foreign Affairs of France |accessdate=2008-02-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071018100421/http://www.diplomatie.gouv.fr/en/country-files_156/brazil_444/france-and-brazil_2515/cultural-scientific-and-technical-cooperation_2634.html |archivedate=2007-10-18 }}</ref>。法國是巴西的第二大科研合作夥伴（僅次於美國）<ref name="Coop10">[http://www.diplomatie.gouv.fr/en/country-files_156/brazil_444/france-and-brazil_2515/cultural-scientific-and-technical-cooperation_7048/index.html Cultural, scientific and technical cooperation] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110622110020/http://www.diplomatie.gouv.fr/en/country-files_156/brazil_444/france-and-brazil_2515/cultural-scientific-and-technical-cooperation_7048/index.html |date=2011-06-22 }} French Ministry of Foreign and European Affairs. Retrieved on 2010-11-29.</ref>，巴西亦是法國在拉丁美洲最大的科研夥伴，兩國在[[氣候變化|氣候變化]]、[[可持續發展|可持續發展]]、[[生物多樣性|生物多樣性]]、創新科技和[[基因|基因]]等研究領域上合作<ref name="Coop10" />。

== 軍事關係 == 
兩國近年來在防務上亦有合作。 2005年7月15日，巴西和法國簽署了多項協議，在先進軍事技術上合作<ref name="MRE">{{cite news|url=http://www2.mre.gov.br/dai/b_fran_177_5544.htm |title=Acordo de Cooperação em Tecnologias Avançadas |publisher=[[Ministry_of_External_Relations_(Brazil)|Ministry of External Relations]] |accessdate=2010-06-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101108060936/http://www2.mre.gov.br/dai/b_fran_177_5544.htm |archivedate=2010-11-08 }}</ref><ref name="MRE2">{{cite news|url=http://www2.mre.gov.br/dai/b_fran_176_5543.htm |title=Acordo para Cooperação na Área da Aeronáutica Militar |publisher=[[Ministry_of_External_Relations_(Brazil)|Ministry of External Relations]] |accessdate=2010-06-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091228162338/http://www2.mre.gov.br/dai/b_fran_176_5543.htm |archivedate=2009-12-28 }}</ref>。2008年，兩國簽訂{{link-en|部隊地位協定|Status of forces agreement}}<ref name="SOFA">{{cite news|url=http://www2.mre.gov.br/dai/b_fran_186.htm |title=Acordo Brasil-França: SOFA |publisher=[[Ministry_of_External_Relations_(Brazil)|Ministry of External Relations]] |accessdate=2010-06-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110716161547/http://www2.mre.gov.br/dai/b_fran_186.htm |archivedate=2011-07-16 }}</ref>；同年12月23日，巴西和法國兩國正式成為戰略聯盟<ref name="MRE3"/>。

巴西和法國在2008年12月24日簽署了一項防務協定<ref>[http://uk.reuters.com/article/governmentFilingsNews/idUKN2354358020081223?pageNumber=1&virtualBrandChannel=0 Brazil, France sign major defense pact] Reuters UK. Retrieved on December 25, 2008.</ref>；同期，巴西總統路易斯·伊納西奧·盧拉·達席爾瓦和法國總統[[薩科齊|薩科齊]]簽署協議，向法國購買50架{{link-en|EC-725直升機|Eurocopter EC725}}、一艘[[核潛艇|核潛艇]]以及4艘[[鮋魚級潛艇|鮋魚級潛艇]]，總值120億美元<ref name=cougar>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/12/24/world/americas/24briefs-BRAZILSIGNSA_BRF.html|title=Brazil Signs Arms Deal With France|publisher=The New York Times|accessdate=2008-12-24|first=Alexei|last=Barrionuevo|date=2008-12-24|archive-date=2020-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200529060453/https://www.nytimes.com/2008/12/24/world/americas/24briefs-BRAZILSIGNSA_BRF.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2009年9月，兩國宣布{{link-en|Agrale|Agrale}}和[[雷諾卡車|雷諾卡車]]將合資生產軍用運輸車輛<ref name="MRE4">{{cite news|url=http://www.itamaraty.gov.br/sala-de-imprensa/notas-a-imprensa/2009/07/visita-ao-brasil-do-presidente-da-franca-nicolas |title=Visita ao Brasil do Presidente da França, Nicolas Sarkozy - Brasília, 6 e 7 de setembro de 2009 - Declaração Conjunta |publisher=[[Ministry_of_External_Relations_(Brazil)|Ministry of External Relations]] |accessdate=2010-06-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110716154310/http://www.itamaraty.gov.br/sala-de-imprensa/notas-a-imprensa/2009/07/visita-ao-brasil-do-presidente-da-franca-nicolas |archivedate=2011-07-16 }}</ref>。

